you just simply setup up few things to make it work
create and .env file in root folder and put these three vairable "MONGODB_URI, PORT, JWT_SECRET".
then go to root folder and run "npm install"
then go to client folder and run "npm install"
after downloading all dependencies
first of all run the server.
go to root folder and hit "npm start"
then go to client folder and hit "npm start".

make sure to correctly define .env file in root folder.
